"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Bivona</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Ferrua recorded as being in Taormina museum, but from Palermo; in reality, it was part of the Museo di S. Martino, now in the Palermo archaeological museum, and original from Rome.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1982.0418 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Ferrua 1941 267 no.35 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002655</a></li><li> Bivona 1970 342 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-3  25-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
